parent.title: Word Of Mouth
parent.description: Ricky Johnson lives a pretty boring existence. He flips burgers by day and watches TV at night. He has no idea a one night stand is about to change his life forever. Beverly Hills is full of rich, horny women who crave fuss-free sex… and are willing to pay more than a pretty penny for it. Thanks to word of mouth, Ricky spends his days pleasing hot housewives and earning big bucks. Can he keep up with the demands of the world’s most privileged women?
